---
/* You can import any images or icons if needed */
---

<section id="about" class="py-20 bg-gray-50 sm:py-28">
  <div class="max-w-6xl px-4 mx-auto sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <!-- Section Title -->
    <div class="text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-extrabold text-gray-900 tracking-tight">
        Who We Are
      </h2>
      <div class="w-24 h-1 mt-4 mx-auto bg-yellow-500 rounded-full"></div>
    </div>

    <!-- Description -->
    <div class="mt-12 max-w-4xl mx-auto text-gray-700 text-lg leading-relaxed space-y-6 text-justify">
      <p>
        Established in <strong>November 2011</strong>, <span class="text-green-900 font-bold">Abhyuday</span> is a premier Project Management Consultancy (PMC) with over a decade of specialized experience in <strong>Agro and Food processing cluster development</strong> and <strong>MoFPI schemes</strong>.
      </p>
      <p>
        With a nationwide reach across <strong>21+ Indian states</strong>, including the North-East, and a global presence with offices in <strong>Japan, USA, and Africa</strong>, our commitment to excellence is reflected in over <strong>₹5,000 Cr of completed projects</strong> and <strong>₹1,000 Cr in ongoing initiatives</strong>.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Stats Grid -->
    <div class="mt-20 grid grid-cols-1 gap-8 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
      {[
        { value: '₹5,000+ Cr', label: 'Completed Projects' },
        { value: '₹1,000 Cr', label: 'Ongoing Projects' },
        { value: '21+ States', label: 'Pan-India Presence' },
        { value: '10+ Years', label: 'MoFPI & Cluster Expertise' },
        { value: 'Global Reach', label: 'Offices in Japan, USA, Africa' },
      ].map((stat) => (
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 p-8 text-center">
          <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900">{stat.value}</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-600">{stat.label}</p>
        </div>
      ))}
    </div>

    <!-- Mission / CTA -->
    <p class="mt-16 text-center text-base italic text-gray-500">
      Empowering the food processing ecosystem — project by project, globally.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

